textBeforeTable: Music Read the full recap Recap The episode begins with Kenzi and Bo fighting a large man, who mentions that the Morrigan “wants the photo”. Eventually the two manage to take down the large man. Kenzi while dragging the large man, tells Bo how this is the third attack on her this week. Their conversation heads in Lauren’s direction and Bo mentions how Kenzi seems to have a problem with Lauren. She asks Kenzi to speak her mind about Lauren. “She is bossy territorial and controlling” Kenzi retorts on being prodded. “She thinks you are immature irresponsible and clingy” Bo says, elaborating what Lauren thinks about Kenzi. ..
